{"data":[{"name":"78:1","price":"Wonach fragen sie sich?","arabic":"عَمَّ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5673,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:2","price":"Nach der gewaltigen Kunde,","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلنَّبَإِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5674,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:3","price":"über die sie sich uneinig sind.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي هُمۡ فِيهِ مُخۡتَلِفُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5675,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:4","price":"Keineswegs! Sie werden (es noch) erfahren.","arabic":"كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5676,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:5","price":"Abermals: Keineswegs! Sie werden (es noch) erfahren.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5677,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:6","price":"Haben Wir nicht die Erde zu einer Lagerstatt gemacht","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ مِهَٰدٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5678,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:7","price":"und die Berge zu Pfählen?","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَوۡتَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5679,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:8","price":"Und Wir haben euch als Paare erschaffen.","arabic":"وَخَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5680,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:9","price":"Und Wir haben euren Schlaf zum Ausruhen gemacht.","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا نَوۡمَكُمۡ سُبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5681,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:10","price":"Und Wir haben die Nacht zum Kleid gemacht.","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلَّيۡلَ لِبَاسٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5682,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:11","price":"Und Wir haben den Tag zur Lebensführung gemacht.","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلنَّهَارَ مَعَاشٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5683,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:12","price":"Und Wir haben über euch sieben feste (Himmel) aufgebaut.","arabic":"وَبَنَيۡنَا فَوۡقَكُمۡ سَبۡعٗا شِدَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5684,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:13","price":"Und Wir haben einen hell glühenden Leuchtkörper gemacht.","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا سِرَاجٗا وَهَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5685,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:14","price":"Und Wir haben von den Regenwolken sich ergießendes Wasser herabkommen lassen,","arabic":"وَأَنزَلۡنَا مِنَ ٱلۡمُعۡصِرَٰتِ مَآءٗ ثَجَّاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5686,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:15","price":"um damit Korn und Gewächse hervorzubringen","arabic":"لِّنُخۡرِجَ بِهِۦ حَبّٗا وَنَبَاتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5687,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:16","price":"und dichtbestandene Gärten.","arabic":"وَجَنَّٰتٍ أَلۡفَافًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5688,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:17","price":"Gewiß, der Tag der Entscheidung ist eine festgesetzte Zeit,","arabic":"إِنَّ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ كَانَ مِيقَٰتٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5689,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:18","price":"der Tag, da ins Horn geblasen wird und ihr in Scharen herkommt","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يُنفَخُ فِي ٱلصُّورِ فَتَأۡتُونَ أَفۡوَاجٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5690,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:19","price":"und da der Himmel geöffnet und dann zu Toren wird","arabic":"وَفُتِحَتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتۡ أَبۡوَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5691,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:20","price":"und da die Berge versetzt und dann zu einer Luftspiegelung werden.","arabic":"وَسُيِّرَتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ فَكَانَتۡ سَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5692,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:21","price":"Gewiß, die Hölle ist ein Hinterhalt,","arabic":"إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتۡ مِرۡصَادٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5693,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:22","price":"für diejenigen, die das Maß (an Frevel) überschreiten, eine Heimstatt,","arabic":"لِّلطَّٰغِينَ مَـَٔابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5694,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:23","price":"lange Zeiten darin zu verweilen;","arabic":"لَّٰبِثِينَ فِيهَآ أَحۡقَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5695,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:24","price":"sie werden darin weder Kühlung noch Getränk kosten,","arabic":"لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرۡدٗا وَلَا شَرَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5696,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:25","price":"außer heißem Wasser und stinkender Brühe,","arabic":"إِلَّا حَمِيمٗا وَغَسَّاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5697,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:26","price":"als angemessene Vergeltung.","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ وِفَاقًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5698,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:27","price":"Sie erwarteten ja niemals eine Abrechnung","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ لَا يَرۡجُونَ حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5699,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:28","price":"und erklärten Unsere Zeichen hartnäckig für Lüge.","arabic":"وَكَذَّبُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا كِذَّابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5700,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:29","price":"Doch alles haben Wir schriftlich erfaßt.","arabic":"وَكُلَّ شَيۡءٍ أَحۡصَيۡنَٰهُ كِتَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5701,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:30","price":"So kostet; Wir werden euch nur die Strafe mehren.","arabic":"فَذُوقُواْ فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمۡ إِلَّا عَذَابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5702,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:31","price":"Gewiß, für die Gottesfürchtigen wird es einen Ort des Erfolgs geben,","arabic":"إِنَّ لِلۡمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5703,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:32","price":"umfriedete Gärten und Rebstöcke","arabic":"حَدَآئِقَ وَأَعۡنَٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5704,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:33","price":"und prächtige, gleichaltrige (weibliche Wesen)","arabic":"وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5705,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:34","price":"und ein (stets) voller Becher.","arabic":"وَكَأۡسٗا دِهَاقٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5706,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:35","price":"Weder hören sie darin unbedachte Rede noch Lüge.","arabic":"لَّا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا كِذَّٰبٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5707,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:36","price":"(Dies) als Belohnung von deinem Herrn, als hinreichende Gabe,","arabic":"جَزَآءٗ مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَآءً حِسَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5708,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:37","price":"dem Herrn der Himmel und der Erde und dessen, was dazwischen ist, dem Allerbarmer. Sie verfügen nicht darüber, vor Ihm zu reden,","arabic":"رَّبِّ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا بَيۡنَهُمَا ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِۖ لَا يَمۡلِكُونَ مِنۡهُ خِطَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5709,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:38","price":"am Tag, da der Geist und die Engel in Reihe stehen. Sie werden nicht sprechen, außer wem der Allerbarmer es erlaubt und wer Richtiges sagt.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلرُّوحُ وَٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ صَفّٗاۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنۡ أَذِنَ لَهُ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابٗا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5710,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:39","price":"Das ist der wahrhaftig (eintreffend)e Tag. Wer nun will, nimmt zu seinem Herrn eine Heimkehr.","arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلۡحَقُّۖ فَمَن شَآءَ ٱتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ مَـَٔابًا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5711,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"},{"name":"78:40","price":"Wir warnen euch ja vor naher Strafe, am Tag, da der Mensch schauen wird, was seine Hände vorausgeschickt haben, und der Ungläubige sagen wird: O wäre ich doch Erde!","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنذَرۡنَٰكُمۡ عَذَابٗا قَرِيبٗا يَوۡمَ يَنظُرُ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مَا قَدَّمَتۡ يَدَاهُ وَيَقُولُ ٱلۡكَافِرُ يَٰلَيۡتَنِي كُنتُ تُرَٰبَۢا","category":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba"],"ayahNumber":5712,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"de"}],"chapter":["78 (An-Naba)","An-Naba","Surah An-Naba","Chapter An-Naba","Naba","Surah Naba","Chapter Naba","An Naba","Surah An Naba","Chapter An Naba","Surah 78","Chapter 78","The Tidings","النبأ"]}